name: South Bow Corporation
longDescription: South Bow is a strategic liquids pipelines company that connects resilient Canadian crude oil supply to the strongest demand and refining markets in the U.S. Midwest and Gulf Coast through its unrivalled corridor, high-quality contractual framework, and investment-grade financial position.
